<section anchor="payload-structures"><name>6. Payload Structures</name>

<t>All structures are packed (no padding). String fields are <strong>null-padded</strong>
fixed-length arrays. Integer fields use the host platform's native
representation for <spanx style="verb">int</spanx> and <spanx style="verb">time_t</spanx> — implementations MUST agree on
endianness and sizes for cross-platform compatibility.</t>

